        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks for <hi rend="italic">Forms of flowers</hi>.</p>  
<p>Alexander Dickson would like to know whether anyone has described the epidermal cells lining the pitcher of <hi rend="italic">Cephalotus</hi>.</p> 
